ygData.messageBody:
Hello,
 
  I am back. I have been gone for awhile. But, for the ones that are new and dont remember me. I am David, I am 29. I play EverQuest on a normal bases. But, right now I havent been on for a while because I had to let my scribes go for the time being. I am planning to get back soon. I want to get the two newiest expanesion. Lancy of Ysheka, and the lost dangunes. Please forgive me I am a bad speller. But I like to keep up with it. I have a question where do you get EQ IM? And, does it cost anythign extra? Is there in thing great about those expanses? I know I have alot of questions. But, I remember that you guys are really helpful, and I am glad. I hope to make some friends that like the samethings I do.
muaddib
